<!-- Banner -->
<div class="banner-peetayers" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%=image_path "https://source.unsplash.com/collection/865018/1000x300"%>');">
  <div class="banner-peetayers-content">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- End Banner -->

<div class="container">
  <div class="body">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="column-1">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3">
          <div class="polaroid flo">
            <div class="polaroid-img" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%=image_path "peetayers/jordan.jpeg" %>');">
            </div>
            <p class="polaroid-text"><strong>Jordan, 26 ans<strong></p>
            <p class="polaroid-desc">"I truly love my town"</p>
          </div>
          <br>

          <div class="infos">
            <div class="infos-title text-center">
              <p><strong>Information checked</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="infos-content">
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Official ID</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Phone</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Email</p></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column-2">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space1 text-center">
              <div class="space1-title">
                <h3>Hello, I'm Jordan!</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="space1-content">
                <p>Lille, France ° for 12 years</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Available services with Franco</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content text-center">
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/suitcase.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Prepare your trip</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Housing services</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Help with admins</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/chat.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Speak local</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Local tips</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/masks.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Cultural outings</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/football.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Play sports</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                      <%= image_tag "flaticon/welcome.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                      <p>Be welcomed</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>French & English</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Why do you like Lille?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>It’s an amazing city, where people are truly welcoming and open-minded. It’s not too busy but you can also alsways find new places and experiences. As an abroad student, it’s perfectly located to travel around Europe.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Lille?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Bars : La Luck, Le Dandy, L’Idiot, Les Frères Pinard, L’Hybride ( Theatre ) Museum : TriPostal and the Musée d’Histoires Naturelles Walk : Le Vieux Lille on Sunday Morning for the Market.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Why do you want to become a Peetayer?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>I love meet new people and new culture. And I truly love Lille and how great the city can be, especially when you’ve never been in France.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>I love Hip-Hop / Trap Music, but I’m also listening other type of music I’m really into Modern Art and Street Art, not too much « Classic » For the rest, I’m passionate by Wine Tasting and Diving.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>What about Jordan?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Jordan is 26 years old and he's freshly gratuated. Currently working as Cybersecurity Consultant in Lille, he loves discover new places and he knows a lot about Southern Asia and Australia.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>Which countries have you visited?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>For work / Studies : Australia, London For travel : Vietnam, Laos, Myanmar, Thailand, Turkey, Cambodia, Philippines, Singapore, Portugal, Poland, Indonesia Next : Japan.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

